{"tid":1818531,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"兔兔獨特的視覺 !","createTime":"2020-01-10T03:46:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T05:07:38.000Z","uid":197098,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5a13aec6a64f094547ff7127edd79b9f68b2c809","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em>側面看某東西就代表正面看某東西</em></span>。牠們正前方和下方是盲點，除了這兩個盲點外，牠們幾乎可以看到360度。(所以有時食物在牠下巴下面睇唔到)&nbsp;<span style=\"color: pink;\"><em>你在牠後面也會看到你</em></span>。兔子只有向著前方大約30度範圍，才可以有立體影像。牠們的脊椎就像軟骨那麼脆弱, 另外也有遠視。所以牠們不是無視你，你是在他們視線範圍之內。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FWGN1HtIEHxA&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=5312d431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/WGN1HtIEHxA</a><br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"986705baadb1a23536b73cf7775a481072b973f0","tid":1818531,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c76fa53a4256e5d4c34c1980db8a4d8fd40c6060","tid":1818531,"uid":343361,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:47:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68a5c5a443ddf71e7ed7849382e86f9b53f03709","tid":1818531,"uid":345551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7eed35444e66ec6cca315be2f45ad8dd960ba477","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68a5c5a443ddf71e7ed7849382e86f9b53f03709","tid":1818531,"uid":345551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"你屋企隻兔？"},{"pid":"49973d20d0f73dd305edddcc733765cb5dbd138f","tid":1818531,"uid":345551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ab6e4ffb33b7fe04b4ec25987eae7bcd0879fc2a","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"49973d20d0f73dd305edddcc733765cb5dbd138f","tid":1818531,"uid":345551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7eed35444e66ec6cca315be2f45ad8dd960ba477","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"68a5c5a443ddf71e7ed7849382e86f9b53f03709","tid":1818531,"uid":345551,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"你屋企隻兔？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T04:45:48.000Z","msg":"可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兔子是被捕獵動物 (prey animals), 是大自然內每個捕獵者 (predators)的目標, 很容易受驚。經常在沙發底因為有安全感，如需要住酒店最好選兔協或其他只給兔子/龍貓住的酒店，因為狗和貓會嚇驚牠"},{"pid":"bcf151d8eee3f0c19535e9ab48f5d1ebdb1e0fe9","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T06:21:07.000Z","msg":"大家有沒有去過<span style=\"color: gold;\">日本「兔仔島」</span>大久野島？這裡有幾千隻自由自在的兔子：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjLnNOtD_sOk&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=503fe599\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jLnNOtD_sOk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyAoXHKDcW8I&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=561fcddd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yAoXHKDcW8I</a><br />\n<br />\n但其實島內, 不是每隻兔子都活得開心和長壽，雖然沒有捕食者(predator)威脅，但很多有病, 沒有足夠糧食和營養, 所以兔迷下次去最好帶乾草(Timothy Hay, Oat Hay, Orchard Hay等)和蔬菜🥬。給牠們最基本的高纖維糧食。不要給高糖份和零食, 例如：蘿蔔、水果。<br />\n<br />\n當兔子<span style=\"color: gold;\">耳朵平放在後面、耳口向下、坐姿躺下/蹲下</span>就代表牠們不開心，耳朵越後就越憂愁。主人就真的要看看究竟做錯什麼事，牠亦可能生病了:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNdKKWbp7U_k&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3e50ce84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NdKKWbp7U_k</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">憂愁</span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0xfQUCe7kp8&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=028c40b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0xfQUCe7kp8</a><br />\n<br />\n這與驚慌(耳朵平放在後面、耳口向側、坐姿蹲下）和憤怒（耳朵和驚慌一樣，但站起來很硬對住你）不同。一個舒適的兔仔會躺下、手腳伸展出來。<br />\n<br />\n兔子因生病(痙攣)而<span style=\"color: gold;\">憂愁</span>:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6OYkOlxe8bM&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=b8e618d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6OYkOlxe8bM</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊來源:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flanguage.rabbitspeak.com%2Falas-woe-is-me&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=11078497\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://language.rabbitspeak.com/alas-woe-is-me</a>"},{"pid":"f5c2b4bf321babc917af250ee868d0df26d8b689","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T08:55:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>兔兔在大自然內的階級觀念</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n在大自然內，兔子有等級制度。一個高級(dominant)的兔子會groom (舔/梳理) 一個次級(inferior)兔子，但高級的亦會要求次級的兔子groom牠。當兔子低頭向前躺在地上，牠是想你groom (撫摸/親吻) 牠，這樣可以增加牠的自尊心、安全感、令牠舒適快樂。當牠們受驚時，也需要groom牠們，令到冷靜下來和知道是沒事的。兔子會騎着另一隻兔背後來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表牠們已決定了等級制度。此行為是正常，無論兩隻是同性或異性。<br />\n<br />\n在0:59 可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyv4VhuZv_s&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c2ae126f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Nyv4VhuZv_s</a><br />\n<br />\n如果你在兔子面前<span style=\"color: gold;\">打開手掌</span>，對於牠來說是要求牠groom 你。如果你們關係好，牠會做。如果牠對主人感到憤怒，對於牠來說是不尊重牠，牠可能會用屁股對着你(代表生悶氣) 或嚴重的話，撲過來咬你。<br />\n<br />\n主人要求兔仔groom 主人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6DKeKyzZ67Y&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=804ca242\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6DKeKyzZ67Y</a><br />\n<br />\n以下兩隻兔子決定等級制度時<span style=\"color: gold;\">遇到困難</span>。一隻 groom另一隻, 但等了很久還未得到回報，所以發脾氣在2:08咬牠。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf7_mGuD5Qg&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=ebe698dc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af7_mGuD5Qg</a><br />\n<br />\n除了騎着兔子背後，兔子還會躺在另一隻兔的頸上來顯示牠是較高層次(show dominance), 此行為停了就代表已決定了等級制度:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fd9WUGogDlg4&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=4f5d5490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/d9WUGogDlg4</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">資訊來源:&nbsp;</span><a href=\"http://rabbitspeak.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frabbitspeak.com&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=f3239828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://rabbitspeak.com</a>&nbsp;(頭3個chapters)"},{"pid":"4b3ea7970d5900d1667d18c8225c19c7416d7f9d","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:13:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子是應該要被絕育....(寵物兔)</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 兔子是被捕獵動物(Prey animal), 是大自然內每個捕獵者(Predator)的目標, 狗吠聲、消防車叫聲、小孩尖叫、雷暴等也會嚇驚兔子, 所以不建議帶出外散步。兔子是全世界其中一個最多被棄養的動物(在美國排第3最多被棄養), 很多人將牠放生, 這樣會令兔子十分恐慌, 而且沒有覓食能力(寵物兔和野兔是不同), 有些人送給兔協, 但容納不到那麼龐大的數目。<br />\n<br />\n2. 絕育後會大大減少因荷爾蒙控制而霸地盤，不會隨地去廁所 (兔子是不需要訓練去廁所，只要廁所內有紙棉和乾草和夠大便可以, 建議用貓廁所)<br />\n<br />\n3. 荷爾蒙減少令攻擊性減少，更加溫馴和親人，也會活得更開心。如果想將2隻兔合養(做夫妻/好朋友)要先絕育才容易建立關係, 否則有機會打架！<br />\n<br />\n4. 兔子是很容易患上生殖器病動物，所以絕育會令到更健康和長壽！<br />\n<br />\n5. 減少過量繁殖(和棄養後所面對的困境)，繁殖得快和多。"},{"pid":"9e5caa8c399c0593fd36cb3625f65e227eb756d9","tid":1818531,"uid":33567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"上朋友屋企成日比佢隻免追著，覺佢先係predator<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4df07928c5d1954fe3b9d7a3c813908565a5915","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e5caa8c399c0593fd36cb3625f65e227eb756d9","tid":1818531,"uid":33567,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:19:03.000Z","msg":"上朋友屋企成日比佢隻免追著，覺佢先係predator<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"親人係好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6a5e9e71ffa33a27af2d67538108d6aa5c254c","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T12:40:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><ins>兔子的食物和份量</ins></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">根據美國兔子協會(House Rabbit Society):</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">每天怎樣餵BB和青少年(7星期-7個月大):</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 1/3 Alfalfa Hay, 2/3 Timothy Hay, 可以加Orchard Hay, Oat Hay 或其他Hay令到更多元化和好味道，任你喜歡😊<br />\n- 2湯匙兔糧：推介Burgess或Oxbow幼兔糧，其他牌子也可以<br />\n- 12個星期大或以上: 開始給吃1-3條手指長的蔬菜 (要徹底清洗)<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>因為消化系統還在生長中，乾草是最重要。喝煲過的冷水，不要給自來水和礦泉水。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">怎樣餵年輕成人(7個月-1歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草: 減少Alfalfa Hay, 增加Timothy Hay和其他Hay<br />\n- 減少到每6磅(兔子體重)半杯兔糧<br />\n- 漸漸地增加蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 極少水果: 每6磅(兔子體重)1-2安士<br />\n<br />\n<strong><em><ins>注意：</ins></em></strong>如果兔子有5磅，未夠6磅，可以盛載半杯兔糧後再倒走1/3或1/4糧，自己調校<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">餵成熟成人(1-5歲)：</span><br />\n- 24小時無限乾草：移除Alfalfa Hay, 只供Timothy Hay, Orchard Hay, Oat Hay等等<br />\n- 每6磅1/4-1/2杯糧<br />\n- 每6磅最少2杯切好的蔬菜🥬<br />\n- 每6磅2安士或以下(2湯匙或以下)水果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">老兔(6歲以上)：</span><br />\n- 如果兔子能夠維持足夠體重，可以繼續供給以上的食法<br />\n- 年老和身體虛弱的需要增加兔糧，體重過輕的可以給吃Alfalfa Hay(前提是體內鈣質正常)。老兔最好定期去驗血。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果我餵很少糧或不餵糧，怎樣補充營養？</span><br />\n- 需要增加蔬菜份量來補充營養，(而卡路里是不需要補充的)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">更多資訊：<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/faq-diet\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Ffaq-diet&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=3fbc5cee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/faq-diet</a></span></span>"},{"pid":"548f36e21900e51ed17af6df98ffb6431dfb637f","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T03:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f170ed99306ef277d4dfcfa5fa7ef80ff679f10a","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T08:49:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2e7860e2a291a67bc2d5f2a82090e55d30d045d","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T16:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad4e8ae1a73e86314fc942cd5561f623107dbb1","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T16:49:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c75f8c4f1c890dd0b2138843e0a6e4b8722d51","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T08:25:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7757ff2936080c3973c1dda1c0369f2bb33bb73e","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T02:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb7cf5bbc71dd7a2b763d4d78488122c267c247","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T07:15:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要同兔子洗澡...</span></span><br />\n<br />\n兔子很愛乾淨，會自動自己清理洗澡。同兔仔洗澡是很危險，會令牠精神創傷，嚇怕到呆和僵硬，經常這樣會心臟病發。但有一個例外: 如果牠們屁股被糞便粘住(poopy butthole), 可以給屁股洗澡🛁(butt bath), 但不要用手直接拉糞便出來，因為會連皮拉出來。要用水浸到肛門和腳然後慢慢清理，不用任何沐浴乳或肥皂:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D6UcoZHBlQ80&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=5ea98312\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6UcoZHBlQ80</a><br />\n<br />\n如果主人試過同兔子洗澡，可能見過兔子用後腳站起來，左右手上下方向擦。這時候兔子其實不是同你玩水，這個姿態是代表不高興，想主人不要理會牠。以下video可看到主人給兔子洗澡時，<span style=\"color: gold;\">兔子在3:26被嚇暈</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6zkyjfOq36g&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=53fbea49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6zkyjfOq36g</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">資訊來源:</span>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frabbit.org%2Fthe-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9f122ceb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rabbit.org/the-dangers-of-giving-a-rabbit-a-bath</a>"},{"pid":"f18beca42169d9f2ffa5e7247695e9dd20a06980","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-16T03:23:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7378f6c657b3aca5e8b17a6c4b546f56db5fc92c","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T02:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d056cf44240a9427afd0e8a81217e32cf671986","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T04:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa471b4a79d04d4187bb8d56599ec994b76c330","tid":1818531,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T02:52:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add4a2e5ae2a83380f78d950747cceafff31a4aa","tid":1818531,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T05:07:38.000Z","msg":"樓主認唔認得我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我係你fd屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}